alence between the quasi-category of maps out of a representable\nfibration and the quasi-category underlying the fiber over its representing\nelement. A companion paper will apply these results to establish a calculus of\nmodules between $\\infty$-categories, which will be used to define and study\npointwise Kan extensions along $\\infty$-functors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jun 2015 21:22:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 14 Oct 2015 15:18:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 13 Jun 2016 06:13:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-14"}
